:false},"created_at":"2025-02-03T11:57:12Z","updated_at":"2025-02-03T11:57:12Z","body":"As with the poster, after setting uids and gids to be the same on both sides, I am no longer picking any files when pressing the rescan button.","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/comments/2630741772/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"astralbat","id":5352772,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzNTI3NzI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5352772?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat","html_url":"https://github.com/astralbat","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astralbat/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/comments/2645580232","html_url":"https://github.com/syncthing/syncthing/issues/9879#issuecomment-2645580232","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/9879","id":2645580232,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAOCAEs6dsFnI","user":{"login":"huanqiugame","id":85951426,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjg1OTUxNDI2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/85951426?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame","html_url":"https://github.com/huanqiugame","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/huanqiugame/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2025-02-08T13:20:31Z","updated_at":"2025-02-08T13:21:20Z","body":"I have installed Syncthing (v1.29.2) on two Macs (absolutely running macOS). What I encountered is that files are continuously syncing, never stopping. I read this issue and turned \"Sync Extended Attributes\" off, and it soon showed me \"Up to Date\". I tested in a separate folder (both in internal and external disks, respectively, including only one file) and confirmed that the issue exists. Here, the only file synced almost every 10 seconds and the \"File Created Time\" was only showed on the device where it was created. In other words, it seemed like that attribute never really synced, causing a difference being noticed by the watcher and showing a 10 seconds interval between every sync.\n\nHowever, things seems to be a little different here. I tried turning on \"Sync Ownership\" and/or \"Sync Extended Attributes\", and found when the latter is turned on, regardless of the former, the issue shows up. It is the \"Sync Extended Attributes\" setting that goes wrong instead of \"Sync Ownership\".\n\nAlso, I can provide additional information if required. Thank you all for working on this issue and the amazing software.","author_association":"NONE","reactions":{